Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.33,0:00:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My birthday?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.70,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, your birthday. When is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:30.60,0:00:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,March 6th, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:33.65,0:00:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your blood type?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.15,0:00:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B type.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.66,0:00:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter centric, Pisces, B type with a wood aspect.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.42,0:00:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is all clear to me now!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.86,0:00:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriyama is a hopeless romantic who always walks her own path!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.14,0:00:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a dreamer{bound to reverie}, but escaping reality in a good way!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.65,0:00:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Izumo?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.26,0:01:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,October 11th... A type.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is all clear to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo is an idealist who interacts equally with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though she's good at adapting to her environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she takes her ideals seriously and often complains about reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune-telling from your star sign, your blood type, and the Four Pillars of Destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it all in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you use your head for useful studies instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, I know you're interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo is really hard to get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me my fortune too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I can't do it for guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only tell the fortune of girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the same to do it for guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares, my birthday is{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you that it won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Satan's son was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiki's birthday is so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,We should organize a surprise{secret} birthday party for Kamiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,Why do we have to celebrate her birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, we decided by majority rule, so don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's decide on everyone's duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you do at a birthday party?{mfw}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be presents... and a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should prepare snacks and drinks too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And decorate the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Presents, huh? I wonder what would make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be some kind of meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbeque{yakiniku} or {cooked beef}sukiyaki or roast beef...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what you'd want to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spit roasted turkey would be nice too... it would fit the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen one in my life though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura, your menu is starting to sound a bit weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A flower bouquet would be nice, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Shima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many edible flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our garden has them too in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you, Moriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:05:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shima arranges the present! Research it and have it ready by Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura prepares the cake! Don't buy one, bake one yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I've never made sweets before though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konekomaru, you do the shopping and act as Okumura's advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriyama and I will decorate the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't half bad at getting stuff done, Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, could I do something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I know how much you love Japanese sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But cakes and Japanese sweets are very different...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best, Konekomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this a secret from everyone. Be very careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A birthday, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Shima! Are you looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, just... Is Paku around?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a word with you? Come with me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, those two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to drag you out here so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, you're so nice, Paku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your looks and your kindness are both top grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura, read the recipe for me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four eggs, 200 grams of sugar, flour...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No-Nothing! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Suguro, you're so good at handicrafts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, well, we're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, Suguro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were chatting during the lunch break like two little birdies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Shima? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really! He just asked me about the upcoming bir{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bir{\fscx250}-{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bird watching tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind then... I was worried because he's such a flirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you making, Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A birthday cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake? What's a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know once you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all that happened...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so awkward to be alone with Okumura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, you sieve the flour and mix it well with the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konekomaru, you're good! You really haven't done this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just watched and learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you too are so good at this, it's hard to believe that this is your first time.{now read these three lines out of context -sometimes I think you're more fujoshi (fudanshi) than I am ww}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good at cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so. There were only guys at our place and everyone sucked at cooking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I had no choice but to do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's a lot more fun to cook for someone else, not just for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make the best cake ever, Konekomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that! The fluff is the life of the dough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it lighter! More gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop!{out of context everywhere}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the message this morning that the herbs I ordered have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, True Cross Academy, Faculty of Pharma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this time it's my personal order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was your idea, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kamiki will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it partially for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny and Mom celebrate my birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this will be the first time I celebrate with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made friends since I started the cram school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought we could all celebrate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's selfish, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, when is your and Rin's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on December 27th.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever had a birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More or less?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so close to Christmas, we always celebrated the two together at the monastery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it never had this birthday feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the party will be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You should come too, Yuki. It'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{CM}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.55,0:11:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,It's just the first try though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,Well, this is my level!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,No way, no way, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,Huh? What about Norway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,There's {\i1}no way{\i0} this'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,Konekomaru! You were supposed to keep an eye him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,I just... looked away for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0025,,Leave Konekomaru alone! It's perfect, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a perfectly fine birthday cake to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So birthday cakes and Christmas cakes are different?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always learn new stuff, even at the age of 15... Right, Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you for your patronage. This is just a small token of our gratitude. Exorcist cram school students.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving a cake celebrating the birth of God... to a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Zwill if you could do some kinda effect to emphasize the "fantastic" it'd be loooovely =3}{\i1}My goodness! It is{\k100} {\kf20\2c&H0000FF&}f{\2c&H00FCFF&\kf20}a{\2c&H00FF0E&\kf20}n{\2c&HF4FF00&\kf20}t{\2c&HFF1000&\kf20}a{\2c&HDD00FF&\kf20}s{\2c&H007BD1&\kf20}t{\2c&HFF0086&\kf20}i{\2c&H007D35&\kf20}c{\2c&H000000&\kf20}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you sure don't need the uniform to be gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I warn you for nothing, Paku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a weirdo, Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're standing too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Izumo was collecting this series.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes charmed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Charmed me... Charmed me... Charmed me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charmed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is whispering too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My heart... My heart.... My heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fell for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going way too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining.{captain obvious}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I don't have an umbrella with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I brought mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharing an umbrella?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got something in my eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one? Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}NOOOOOO!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She found us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"She found us out", my ass! You and you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you try to k...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kiss Paku here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't! I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what were you doing so close to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were looking for your birthday pre{\fscx250}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:16:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how she found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously this stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you just use me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're just using me to have your little fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo, you should be happy rather than...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it was my idea to make a surprise party...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to apologize for. Moriyama wanted to make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is celebrating your birthday such a nuisance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying that it's unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfair to start celebrating birthdays now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about everyone who's had their birthday after we started school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:17:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of us has to be 16 already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you guys were talking about scooter licenses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too sharp, Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to do this, then do it properly for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise I won't take part in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Bon and Shima and Kamiki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Paku too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means four presents?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll give back the collected money to Suguro and Shima... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is turning into a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's throw a party for everyone, even for those who have their birthdays later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to write this in hiragana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a moment, I'll spell it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-A-P-P-Y.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have your drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura made that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's the only productive thing I'm good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said it himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konekomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Konekomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All together... {OMG i thought hanakana's gonna go "demo sonna n ja dame mou sonna n ja hora kokoro wa shinka suru yo motto motto for a second"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the presents we all have been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll decide who gets what by lottery!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about how much fun everyone's having.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been so weird lately, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been told that our birthday is December 27th, but it doesn't really mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows who gave birth to us when and where.{say what? that was so totally a couple eps ago -ikr}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of a person was our mom?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I picked you kids up under a bridge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was midwinter but this huuuge watermelon was floating in the river.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I opened it, you guys were inside!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriously?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't really know which way I should cut the melon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't do it right, so I accidentally cut you into two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father was always using stupid excuses and he never told us the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I first met you two on a snowy day like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only clue I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we have no way to figure out our true birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is so cool!{fancy}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, thanks for being born!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when you were born, I'm happy you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two have numbers 2 and 7 left, take your picks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.15,0:23:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It suits you perfectly! It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's a birthday party!{rin in the background}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Understood. I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.51,0:23:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Yukio?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our monastery was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.01,0:23:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{CM you MUST leave that bushiroad one}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.92,0:24:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let anyone get hurt because of me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.07,0:24:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going anywhere today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the fuss about, Yukio?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.03,0:24:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, you're still trying to...{i couldn't fit my brother here, hell yeah svo}
