Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.28,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,kizu darake ni natte try for pride
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:10.78,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{ah, ah, ah, alone in my world}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.41,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}soredemo ai wo utau
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:15.62,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,hizunda sekai todokazu negai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:18.46,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,kizuki ageteku kizuna to ashita
