Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:25.09,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,430)}{it's my precious life}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.55,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{Dark cloud in my heart is}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.51,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,harewatari michi ni hikari wa sashita
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:33.39,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight osore wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:37.02,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,820)}moroha no tsurugi furikazashita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{English}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:25.69,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark side in my heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:28.28,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,the unerasable sadness of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:30.49,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright if I don't really mean it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:33.24,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,430)}so I fire my blasters and stretch out my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:38.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,230)}Since when has my way been unavoidable like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:42.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(280,400)}And now there's no one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.42,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck this destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:48.05,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I cry for my pride, I can't bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:50.55,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, ah, ah, alone in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.51,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}An aria of love resounding through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:55.22,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,this distorted reality of twisted prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:58.06,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreams and tomorrow are collapsing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:01.73,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,230)}because throwing away the lies would be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.82,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,430)}Good bye precious life.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.53,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}Go and repaint this destiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.28,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,try it for your pride, covered in wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:10.78,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, ah, ah, alone in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.41,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I sing the song of love and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:15.62,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,let its wish reach through this distorted world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:18.46,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,to build our bonds and the tomorrow to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)}Throwing away the lies was important after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:25.09,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,430)}because this is my precious life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.55,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark cloud in my heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.51,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,disappearing and light is shining on the road I'm on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:33.39,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight, there's no fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:37.02,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,820)}I brandished my two-edged sword.
