Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:23.23,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and there I notice a terrible error.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:27.02,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Connecting people to one another
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:30.53,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}is a shining pale indigo blue wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.49,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's beautiful like a thread of silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:38.66,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder if it's what they call the chains of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.66,0:22:41.95,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You seek for it and yet you're already caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:43.87,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so don't try to struggle.
